  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Alys</b> is a Westerosi given name. It may refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Arryn_(wife_of_Rhaegel)\" title=\"Alys Arryn (wife of Rhaegel)\">Alys Arryn</a>, wife of Prince Rhaegel Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Arryn\" title=\"Alys Arryn\">Alys Arryn</a>, sister to Lord Jon Arryn</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Beesbury\" title=\"Alys Beesbury\">Alys Beesbury</a>, wife to Ser Leo Tyrell</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Frey\" title=\"Alys Frey\">Alys Frey</a>, wife to her cousin Ser Jared Frey, the fourth son of Lord Walder Frey</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Harroway\" title=\"Alys Harroway\">Alys Harroway</a>, wife to Maegor I Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Karstark_(wife_of_Brandon)\" title=\"Alys Karstark (wife of Brandon)\">Alys Karstark</a>, wife of Lord Brandon Stark</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Karstark\" title=\"Alys Karstark\">Alys Karstark</a>, the only daughter of Lord Rickard Karstark</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Oakheart\" title=\"Alys Oakheart\">Alys Oakheart</a>, wife to Ser Jon Cafferen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Rivers\" title=\"Alys Rivers\">Alys Rivers</a>, bedmate to Prince Aemond Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Stackspear\" title=\"Alys Stackspear\">Alys Stackspear</a>, the first wife of Ser Jason Lannister</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Stark\" title=\"Alys Stark\">Alys Stark</a>, the second daughter of Lord Cregan Stark</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Stone\" title=\"Alys Stone\">Alys Stone</a>, the eldest bastard daughter of Ser Harrold Hardyng</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Turnberry\" title=\"Alys Turnberry\">Alys Turnberry</a>, a lady companion to Princess Saera Targaryen</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1